#macro (radioline $label $name $labels $values $sep)
  #set( $value = "" )
  #set( $value = $data.get($name) )
  #set($i=0)
  <tr><td valign='top'>
  #if ( $error.get($name) == "NullOrEmpty" )
    <font color='#ff0000;'>
    #else
    <font>
  #end
    $label
    </font>
</td><td valign='top'>
  #set($i=0)
  #foreach ($v in $values) 
    <input type='radio' name='$name' value ='$v'#if("$v"=="$value") checked='checked'#end >
    $labels.get($i) $!sep
    #set($i=1+$i)
  #end
</td></tr>
#end

#macro (radiolineI $label $name $labels $values)
  #set( $value = "" )
  #set( $value = $data.get($name) )
  #set($i=0)
  <tr><td valign='top'>
  #if ( $error.get($name) == "NullOrEmpty" )
    <font color='#ff0000;'>
    #else
    <font>
  #end
    $label
    </font>
</td><td valign='top'>
  $labels.get(0) 
  #set($i=0)
  #foreach ($v in $values) 
    <input type='radio' name='$name' value ='$v'#if("$v"=="$value") checked='checked'#end >
    #set($i=1+$i)
  #end
  $labels.get(1) 
</td></tr>
#end
